{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt nur wenige L\u00e4nder weltweit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen Jugendliche so gute Zukunftschancen haben wie hier in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Jugendarbeitslosigkeit liegt bei gut 6\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist europaweit eine der niedrigsten Quoten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.280", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein wesentlicher Grund f\u00fcr diesen Erfolg ist unsere duale Berufsausbildung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie bietet jedes Jahr mehr als einer halben Million junger Menschen die Chance auf einen erfolgreichen Einstieg in die Berufswelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will mit einigen konkreten Zahlen aus dem Berufsbildungsbericht beginnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr dieses Ausbildungsjahr hat die Wirtschaft \u00fcber 556\u00a0000\u00a0Stellen angeboten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.800", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind 10\u00a0000 mehr als im vergangenen Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "523\u00a0000\u00a0Ausbildungsvertr\u00e4ge wurden neu abgeschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.200", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit haben wir endlich wieder mehr Auszubildende."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders stark war die Zunahme der betrieblich geschlossenen Ausbildungsvertr\u00e4ge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort ist die Zahl um fast 5\u00a0000 gestiegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "100\u00a0Bewerbern standen also zuletzt 105\u00a0Ausbildungsangebote gegen\u00fcber. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.360", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Chancen auf einen Ausbildungsplatz sind so gut wie seit mehr als 20\u00a0Jahren nicht mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine stolze Leistung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir hier gemeinsam erbracht haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich pers\u00f6nlich bin froh \u00fcber diese Art der Zusammenarbeit zwischen Wirtschaft und Staat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir im Bereich der beruflichen Bildung leisten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Europa und weltweit sind wir damit eine der f\u00fchrenden Berufsbildungsnationen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daran besteht kein Zweifel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch gibt sich diese Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gebe ich mich pers\u00f6nlich damit nicht zufrieden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.320", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen noch besser werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den vergangenen Jahren haben wir sehr auf die Hochschulen geschaut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist die berufliche Bildung im Verst\u00e4ndnis der jungen Menschen ein wenig ins Hintertreffen geraten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei sollen die sogenannten Abbrecherquoten f\u00fcr mich nicht das gr\u00f6\u00dfte Problem sein; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.360", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn trotz vieler Falschmeldungen ist es tats\u00e4chlich so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.160", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Zahl der Ausbildungsabbr\u00fcche sehr viel niedriger ist als im Hochschulbereich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.760", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zudem\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.280", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das m\u00f6chte ich hier auch sagen\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.040", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Vertragsl\u00f6sung mit Neubeginn ist eine freie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.520", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "individuelle Entscheidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir verteidigen und gerade nicht kritisieren sollten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wichtig ist doch nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass den jungen Menschen die T\u00fcr ge\u00f6ffnet bleibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sehe die Herausforderungen in der beruflichen Bildung vor allem in drei Bereichen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen wieder mehr Jugendliche f\u00fcr die berufliche Bildung begeistern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.120", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.760", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen die berufliche Bildung fit machen f\u00fcr eine moderne digitalisierte Arbeitswelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen wieder mehr Betriebe f\u00fcr die Ausbildung gewinnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum ersten Punkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.840", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass alle jungen Menschen in unserem Land die Chance haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.480", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Talente zu entfalten und erfolgreich ins Berufsleben zu starten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr gibt es viele M\u00f6glichkeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je nach Neigung und F\u00e4higkeiten m\u00fcssen sich junge Menschen f\u00fcr ihren Weg entscheiden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.160", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.400", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihnen dabei bewusst ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Akademische Bildung und berufliche Bildungswege sind gleichwertige Bildungswege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade in dieser Zeit der schnellen Entwicklungen ist die enge Verzahnung von Theorie und Praxis eine solide Basis f\u00fcr die eigene berufliche Karriere. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00f6chte ich noch st\u00e4rker im Bewusstsein der Menschen verankern\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei den jungen Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch bei den Eltern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem gilt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.920", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Bildungssystem ist durchl\u00e4ssig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.160", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer eine Ausbildung macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.880", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann sp\u00e4ter studieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer mit einem Studium beginnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann f\u00fcr die Weiterbildung die beruflichen Weiterbildungsstufen nutzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.720", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Karrierechancen in der beruflichen Bildung m\u00f6chte ich noch weiter verbessern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn gerade auch Leistungstr\u00e4ger sollen in der beruflichen Bildung gef\u00f6rdert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.200", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden klare und attraktive Fortbildungsstufen im Berufsbildungsgesetz etablieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit Personalabteilungen sofort erkennen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Kompetenzen eine Kandidatin oder ein Kandidat mitbringt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.200", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden das Aufstiegs-BAf\u00f6G mit einem attraktiven Angebot f\u00fcr jede Stufe ausbauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das sorgt f\u00fcr Gleichwertigkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.840", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte an dieser Stelle auch die Mindestausbildungsverg\u00fctung ansprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.720", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ist ein klares Signal der Wertsch\u00e4tzung f\u00fcr die duale Ausbildung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.840", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gilt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.400", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "soziale Schieflagen zu adressieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.400", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All das zeigt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.360", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gleichwertigkeit der beruflichen Bildung steht f\u00fcr diese Bundesregierung ganz oben auf der bildungspolitischen Agenda, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.080", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nur abstrakt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.000", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern mit klaren Schritten und konkreten Verbesserungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.600", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch die jungen Menschen m\u00fcssen sich bewegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.440", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insgesamt blieben zum 30.\u00a0September 2017 fast 50\u00a0000\u00a0Ausbildungsstellen unbesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.640", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur gleichen Zeit standen fast 25\u00a0000\u00a0Jugendliche ohne Ausbildungsplatz da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.400", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "344.280", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir m\u00fcssen den jungen Menschen sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "344.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "348.520", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine solide Ausbildung immer einen guten Start ins Leben bedeutet."
   ]
